Replication of a research claim from Benjamin et al, 2010, in American Economic Review 
2. Authors and affiliations  
RR TEAM INSTRUCTIONS: ​Fill in the names and affiliations of your team below​. 
 
Nathan Fiala - Associate Professor, Department of Agricultural and Resource Economics, 
