Due to concerns regarding the COVID-19 pandemic, we will conduct these experiments online 
through a non-probabilistic survey to comply with social distancing. The target population being 
sampled will be Asian Americans. A pool of 450 Asian Americans will be sampled, along with a 
sample drawn from the general white American population of equal size. There will be gender 
parity in these two samples to account for gender as a confounding variable.  
 
